209
00:12:36.600 --> 00:12:37.920
Thank you, Ross.

210
00:12:37.920 --> 00:12:39.840
Good afternoon everyone.

211
00:12:39.840 --> 00:12:41.920
What happened to me was that

212
00:12:41.920 --> 00:12:44.920
I actually trusted a friend,

213
00:12:44.920 --> 00:12:47.360
someone that was very close to me

214
00:12:47.360 --> 00:12:48.600
who was like a brother.

215
00:12:48.600 --> 00:12:49.320
We were so close.

216
00:12:49.320 --> 00:12:51.920
He was like an older brother to me.

217
00:12:51.920 --> 00:12:54.720
And I had borrowed him some money.

218
00:12:54.720 --> 00:12:58.560
It was something as little as,
I think, £50 or something.

219
00:12:58.640 --> 00:13:00.920
I had just finished sixth form college.

220
00:13:00.920 --> 00:13:06.560
I was going into uni and
I borrowed him £50.

221
00:13:06.560 --> 00:13:10.840
He said he needed it desperately
and in the past I've helped him.

222
00:13:10.840 --> 00:13:11.720
He's helped me.

223
00:13:11.720 --> 00:13:13.280
We had like a good relationship.

224
00:13:13.280 --> 00:13:17.080
So I had no reason to think
anything of it.

225
00:13:17.160 --> 00:13:19.600
So I borrowed him the £50

226
00:13:19.600 --> 00:13:22.600
and then I kept asking him, you know,
when will you pay me back?

227
00:13:22.600 --> 00:13:25.680
It  took a while for
him to pay me back.

228
00:13:25.880 --> 00:13:29.520
And then one day, when he
was ready to pay me back,

229
00:13:29.520 --> 00:13:35.200
he called me and told me that he has
paid me back into my bank account

230
00:13:35.200 --> 00:13:39.640
because he had asked me for my bank
account a few weeks before that.

231
00:13:39.720 --> 00:13:44.240
And then I, you know, I went to
the bank, not on the same day.

232
00:13:44.240 --> 00:13:47.840
I can't remember
exactly the timescale,

233
00:13:47.840 --> 00:13:53.120
but I eventually went to the bank to go
withdraw some change out

234
00:13:53.120 --> 00:13:55.920
so that I can buy some
things for my son and I, 

235
00:13:55.920 --> 00:13:59.160
because I had just become a
teenage mum as well at that time.

236
00:13:59.640 --> 00:14:05.440
And it's important to note that
this account was a savings account,

237
00:14:05.440 --> 00:14:08.080
it was a passbook account.

238
00:14:08.080 --> 00:14:10.800
Therefore, I had no access to online banking.

