00:41:37.320 --> 00:41:41.800
And the second one is
the ‘Don't Be Fooled’ campaign.

719
00:41:41.800 --> 00:41:45.960
So Don't Be Fooled is a collaboration
between UK finance and Cifas.

720
00:41:45.960 --> 00:41:50.560
It aims to inform students or young people
about the risks of giving out their bank details

721
00:41:50.560 --> 00:41:53.560
and deter them from becoming money mules.

722
00:41:53.560 --> 00:41:57.200
So lots of great content again.
There’s an excellent short video

723
00:41:57.200 --> 00:42:01.000
that you can play to young people,
which really highlights the dangers,

724
00:42:01.000 --> 00:42:04.760
the consequences that
you need to think about.

725
00:42:04.760 --> 00:42:09.520
So do have a look at the Don't
Be Fooled websites as well.

726
00:42:10.080 --> 00:42:12.000
Now, as we draw to a close,

727
00:42:12.000 --> 00:42:15.760
I'm now just going to move on
to what we feel

728
00:42:15.760 --> 00:42:19.840
are some really key takeaways
both from Sam and Ebony.

729
00:42:19.840 --> 00:42:23.960
So first of all, we've heard lots from you Sam,

730
00:42:23.960 --> 00:42:26.880
lots of insight, lots of guidance,
lots of work we're doing.

731
00:42:26.880 --> 00:42:30.440
But what would be your key takeaways
for the audience?

732
00:42:30.880 --> 00:42:32.120
Yeah, thank you Ross.

733
00:42:32.120 --> 00:42:35.000
 So my main takeaways would be that

734
00:42:35.000 --> 00:42:38.360
if you're receiving any money into your account,

735
00:42:38.360 --> 00:42:40.920
make sure that you know
where those funds are coming from.

736
00:42:40.920 --> 00:42:42.400
And don't be afraid to question

737
00:42:42.400 --> 00:42:45.360
the person who's paying it to you,
even those you trust,

738
00:42:45.360 --> 00:42:49.000
given Ebony's experience,
unfortunately.

739
00:42:49.000 --> 00:42:53.680
A genuine person won't mind
a little bit of questioning.

740
00:42:53.680 --> 00:42:56.800
It's valid in today's environment.

741
00:42:56.800 --> 00:43:00.640
The second item would be to be really wary

742
00:43:00.640 --> 00:43:04.680
of urgent requests,
particularly to withdraw funds.

743
00:43:04.680 --> 00:43:07.160
Just pay to you really at speed.

744
00:43:07.160 --> 00:43:11.320
Mules absolutely need to operate quickly

745
00:43:11.320 --> 00:43:15.600
to move their criminal proceeds
around the financial ecosystem.

746
00:43:15.600 --> 00:43:19.440
And you'll just be supporting
them if you do that.

747
00:43:19.440 --> 00:43:21.920
So don't make it easy for them,

748
00:43:21.920 --> 00:43:24.720
you know, be very wary of those types of request.

749
00:43:24.720 --> 00:43:26.000
That would be it for me.

750
00:43:26.000 --> 00:43:26.920
Thanks Ross.

751
00:43:26.920 --> 00:43:28.400
Over to you Ebony.

752
00:43:30.480 --> 00:43:32.400
Thanks Sam.

753
00:43:32.400 --> 00:43:36.440
For me, yep, be careful who you trust.

754
00:43:36.440 --> 00:43:40.320
Friends and family could
be recruited by criminals,

755
00:43:40.320 --> 00:43:45.720
so be very careful when doing
favours that involve money.

756
00:43:45.720 --> 00:43:47.760
Always check your account regularly.

757
00:43:47.760 --> 00:43:50.440
Obviously, in my case,
I couldn't check my account regularly

758
00:43:50.440 --> 00:43:53.760
because I did not have access to online
bank or mobile banking.

759
00:43:53.760 --> 00:43:56.160
But nowadays, most of us do

760
00:43:56.160 --> 00:44:00.080
so please check your accounts regularly,
your bank statements check them regularly

761
00:44:00.080 --> 00:44:03.200
just to see, you know, where
money's coming from.

762
00:44:03.200 --> 00:44:05.040
You might not be expecting
some form of money.

763
00:44:05.040 --> 00:44:07.440
Make sure you contact
your bank immediately

764
00:44:07.440 --> 00:44:10.680
to find out where it came from
before spending it.

765
00:44:10.680 --> 00:44:16.600
Because if you withdraw or transfer
any money that comes from

766
00:44:16.600 --> 00:44:20.640
a criminal source, you will be,
you know, punished, like in my case.

767
00:44:20.640 --> 00:44:23.400
And then the last thing is

768
00:44:23.400 --> 00:44:27.400
do not be fooled by the thought
of making quick money.

769
00:44:27.400 --> 00:44:30.520
You know, there's a cost of
living crisis right now,

770
00:44:30.520 --> 00:44:33.560
so if you are looking for an extra
income, contact your local jobcentre

771
00:44:33.560 --> 00:44:36.640
because there are various job
opportunities out there.

772
00:44:37.840 --> 00:44:39.640
Over to you Ross.

