mules used to visit the school gates.

779
00:45:00.120 --> 00:45:02.720
They used to approach
young people in person.

780
00:45:02.720 --> 00:45:03.960
The world has changed.

781
00:45:03.960 --> 00:45:06.680
The use of technology
means that actually people

782
00:45:06.680 --> 00:45:10.840
people can now sit behind a laptop,
they can sit behind a phone.

783
00:45:10.840 --> 00:45:15.080
They can do this targeting of
young people in a different way,

784
00:45:15.080 --> 00:45:18.720
which obviously makes
it even harder to catch these people.

785
00:45:18.720 --> 00:45:20.800
So I think that's something
we really need to bear in mind.

786
00:45:20.800 --> 00:45:24.120
Young people are exposed to so much online.

787
00:45:24.120 --> 00:45:27.400
Social media has a real
part to play in terms of

788
00:45:27.400 --> 00:45:31.640
what we see being shared
 in terms of adverts, posts

789
00:45:31.640 --> 00:45:34.560
but in the meantime, we just
really need to make sure

790
00:45:34.560 --> 00:45:37.960
that young people are aware
of how they can be targeted.

